data.description: **VRM pricing, sellers will entertain offers between $190,000 and $210,500**    Welcome to 6710 Highmont Dr! This adorable ranch style brick home is waiting for you! Nestled on a beautiful, spacious lot, this 3 bedroom 2 bath home has a lot to offer! When you first arrive you will notice a beautiful large front yard and plenty of room for parking if you like to entertain. When you first walk in you will enter into a formal living room area. Of course you can use this space as a bonus room or office space. To the right you can also enter into the formal dining area OR turn that space into a large walk in pantry because it connects to the kitchen! From the front door if you keep walking straight you will enter into the sweet, cozy living room with a view to the large backyard. Living Room features a beautiful brick fireplace perfect for the fall and winter season coming up. Laundry room is very spacious and even has backyard access. Use this large space in the laundry room as a mud room and extra storage too! On the other side of the house are the 3 spacious bedrooms and two bathrooms. Now lets talk about the back patio and backyard! The back patio is oversized and covered, perfect for parties or if it is raining the kids can still play outside. The back yard is fenced and gets plenty of sunlight if you want to have a garden or a pool, there is plenty of room. When you're outside you'll notice how peaceful it sounds, birds chirping and the sound of the wind blowing through the trees, you will definitely want to sit out here and drink your coffee or beverage of choice. This home is waiting for you! Conveniently located to schools and interstate access, schedule a showing today!
